OL,5, Women working at Australia's research  
OL,6, camps in Antarctica have endured       
OL,7, widespread sexual harassment, a report 
OL,8, has found.                             
OL,10,FIt described evidence of uninvited     
OL,11,Ftouching, requests for sex, and a      
OL,12,Fpredatory" culture which condoned      
OL,13,Fpornography on walls and sexual taunts.
OL,15,FWoman also felt they had to hide their 
OL,16,Fmenstruation, and ration tampons and   
OL,17,Fpads because they were so limited.     
OL,19,FOfficials have condemned the findings  
OL,20,Fand vowed to bring on cultural change. 
